Package de.adorsys.datasafe.types.api.resource

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PrivateResource
    The interface that represents some private resource location relative to some container (resource root).
    PublicResource
    Interface to be used for public (shareable) resource paths.
    ResolvedResource
    Interface used as output from operations with storage.
    ResourceLocation<T>
    Interface for resource path, both physical and logical that may contain extra information like file metadata.
    Version
    Base interface that means some version tag, example: commit id.
    Versioned<T,S,V extends Version>
    Interface that identifies object that may have versions.
    VersionedResourceLocation<T,V extends Version>
